{"type":"answer","id":236442,"parentType":"question","parentId":23283,"uid":11531,"contents":"看着爽但是实则给台海局势添了把火，不是件好事。墙内民气高涨，指不定梁家河博士脑抽就一声令下直接打过去。共军大头兵命便宜，但是国军命贵，折腾不起的。<br>\n<br>\n军舰也一样。共军大工厂，原材料多，虽然质量粗劣，但是坏了就再来一个，根本不怕消耗。国军小工厂，美式技术，但是持续性不行。我只能希望这次着火能被一些共军中层官僚混过去，别搞大。要不然梁家河博士大手一挥，坏了一个，加预算，再来十个，那可危险了。<br>\n<br>\n以上只是不懂军事的人的朴素的看法。。。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/ZJbRo1.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/ZJbRo1.png\" alt=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/ZJbRo1.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/esmM0u.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/esmM0u.png\" alt=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/esmM0u.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/CaYmkG.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/CaYmkG.png\" alt=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/11/CaYmkG.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-12","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":7}